title: Business of Sports: Fantasy Football Week 4 (Podcast)

description:
Michael Barr, Rich Trueman, and Damian Sassower bring you the Bloomberg Business of Sports Fantasy Podcast. The trio breaks down week 4 of the NFL season and gets you ready for gameday!
